{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YFdr4tYvmYTAfFHQz9kwdd","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# space-architect-server\n2\t\n3\tSpace: `20260622-space-architect-server`\n4\tCreated: 2026-06-22T00:12:45-06:00\n5\t\n6\t## Organization\n7\t\n8\t- `space.yaml` tracks the space identity, status, and associated metadata.\n9\t- `repos/` contains cloned Git repositories for this work.\n10\t- `notes/` is for task notes, scratch docs, and thinking-in-progress.\n11\t- `architecture/` holds the architect mission memory (ARCHITECT.md and the per-iteration files).\n12\t- `tmp/` is the workspace-local scratch directory. Use it instead of `/tmp` or\n13\t  `/var/tmp`; when using `mktemp`, use `tmp/` as the base directory.\n14\t- `build/` holds the architect loop's per-lane worktrees and scratch\n15\t  (gitignored except `.keep`).\n16\t- The space is a Git repository so notes and architecture are versioned.\n17\t  `repos/`, `tmp/`, and `build/` are gitignored, keeping the cloned repos and scratch\n18\t  out of the space's history (each clone keeps its own Git repo).\n19\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"73957b96-3094-4181-9d71-3a571586c13a","uuid":"ff9fd9b9-3a43-4045-a62a-5bdc74ad9b00","timestamp":"2026-06-22T08:06:38.631Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/ci/space-architect-server/README.md","content":"# space-architect-server\n\nSpace: `20260622-space-architect-server`\nCreated: 2026-06-22T00:12:45-06:00\n\n## Organization\n\n- `space.yaml` tracks the space identity, status, and associated metadata.\n- `repos/` contains cloned Git repositories for this work.\n- `notes/` is for task notes, scratch docs, and thinking-in-progress.\n- `architecture/` holds the architect mission memory (ARCHITECT.md and the per-iteration files).\n- `tmp/` is the workspace-local scratch directory. Use it instead of `/tmp` or\n  `/var/tmp`; when using `mktemp`, use `tmp/` as the base directory.\n- `build/` holds the architect loop's per-lane worktrees and scratch\n  (gitignored except `.keep`).\n- The space is a Git repository so notes and architecture are versioned.\n  `repos/`, `tmp/`, and `build/` are gitignored, keeping the cloned repos and scratch\n  out of the space's history (each clone keeps its own Git repo).\n","numLines":19,"startLine":1,"totalLines":19}}}
